{"tid":630084,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企有死雀，點算","createTime":"2018-04-15T09:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T10:46:15.000Z","uid":143010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a38ccd8a17977b8bb3786caf62f42114aabaf356","tid":630084,"uid":143010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:29:51.000Z","msg":"我間房最近有雀仔成日飛去放冷氣機槽嗰位<br />\n今日企上去睇下 點知有隻好虛弱咁停左係度<br />\n家姐又好驚 叫我整走佢<br />\n咁我就揾左碌棍想推走佢<br />\n一開窗就有陣好臭嘅味飄入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來唔靜只一隻雀係度 仲有隻死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日又係星期日 漁護署電話冇人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家好撚驚 好驚有病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/172914_1ffe4d9ec7451ffcf682fa92b1b441e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F172914_1ffe4d9ec7451ffcf682fa92b1b441e8.jpg&h=c3e912e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原諒我張相咁濛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n紅圈係死雀 藍圈係就死嘅雀<br />\n我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b56f79c48760f750ac457677cc71bc5489ffdc","tid":630084,"uid":36670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:30:45.000Z","msg":"打1823"},{"pid":"2ab909c713ba22ad7eea96918c55683feafaaeb2","tid":630084,"uid":143010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:31:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打1823</blockquote><br />\n打過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇人聽"},{"pid":"74b5ae49cbe9f8ce773e1ff5b52bd443d4adf49a","tid":630084,"uid":36670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ab909c713ba22ad7eea96918c55683feafaaeb2","tid":630084,"uid":143010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:31:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquot